exercise.p:

In Finland only the adults (18 yrs) are allowed to play coin slot machines. Make a program that will test whether the user is old enough to play. 

The idea of the code:

function checkAge() {
    // assign the age input field value into a variable 
    if (age smaller than 18) { 
        // Write to the page: "Adolescents are not allowed to play."  
    }
    otherwise { 
        // Write to the page: "Old enough to play."   
    } 
} 

Call the checkAge()-function when the Check player’s age –button’s onclick event occurs.
